{"tid":1553569,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"10點窗邊研討會","createTime":"2019-09-08T15:54:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T16:39:54.000Z","uid":203413,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a20e4cc5fba3f0233c540a46f6daf7af5fcaf871","tid":1553569,"uid":203413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:54:00.000Z","msg":"十點活動係最低成本抗爭，如果突然有一晚大家唔洗再叫既，咁樣只有正明兩件事。<br />\n<br />\n1.<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>抗爭成功</strong></span><br />\n2.香港人放棄<br />\n<br />\n我知要一直叫，真係太攰。甚至聲線受損，影響日常生活。雖然，為咗抗爭影響日常生活在所難免。但keep住叫唔係一個令 10點窗口 最持久既方法，相反可能出現疲態。<br />\n<br />\n所以我諗將嚟個活動昇華，去到一個keep到抗爭熱度，同時又傳遞訊息既抗爭。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n照舊10點鐘響炮。一班人叫一陣，唔需要長。因為只係要比手足知道，仍然有同路人。同話比香港人知，仍然有人抗爭。<br />\n<br />\n之後就係重點。我地要傳承訊息。我地要尋找屋苑入邊嘅靚聲王去講一啲資訊。我地五大訴求，邊五大？之後講針對唔同方面嘅題目，去傳遞重要資訊（唔洗長，但一個鐘入邊重複講幾次），例如：中國既經濟來源，係點樣吸香港既血。中國行既每一步係點樣去剝削香港。送中既結果、被定性暴動嘅結果、唔識放手足既結果、無獨立調查委員會既結果等等.... 題目唔洗一次過講，分開。每日唔同講法，唔同話題。你講果陣佢地可以聽，慢慢反洗佢地腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n咁以下係我諗到既on9宣揚：<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n各位香港市民，晚安。我地係香港一班抗爭者想向咁多香港人講既說話。<br />\n<br />\n我地都係一班愛香港既市民，我地追求自由、平等、法治、公義。我地明白近日既自發行動為咁多位帶來不便。係到向咁多位致歉。<br />\n<br />\n但現在政府仍然向五大訴求給出假希望。我地五大訴求係......<br />\n<br />\n（之後就五選一）<br />\n而政府針對獨立調查委員會訴求作出既行動，仍然依賴監警會。（之後我唔識講，總之講佢點解無用同信唔過）<br />\n<br />\n（可以講下聽日既集會，遊行）<br />\n<br />\n最後，不設不散。（果日題目關於釋放手足既話就講「沒有暴徒，只有暴政」）<br />\n光復香港，時代革命。<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n文章最好係網上立法會（連登）投稿。<br />\n每日新鮮滾熱辣。<br />\n嚟個只有和理非先參與到，同時我地和理非最有作用就係keep住抗爭熱力，同盡我哋所能招攬民意，令佢地同我地一齊抗爭。到一日佢地都係窗邊大叫口號。<br />\n<br />\n我咁諗得唔得先？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f65e031ca1398134c65932eb03a1f7bbc88be14","tid":1553569,"uid":7003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:54:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cDUYBsp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcDUYBsp.png&h=fdb19aa9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n何文田區學校 舊生街坊學生connect!"},{"pid":"59b7f115a5efd4ef3d1a7e687e04db8c9f3f6f69","tid":1553569,"uid":227981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:55:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9qD0StPLq6M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D9qD0StPLq6M&d=h%2B0F1AfFk4MBaO73S6qK%2BpFDRn80AWZfiUxX1c6OkmY%3D&h=d079ec35\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9qD0StPLq6M</a>"},{"pid":"92cd86bc7edba1bab5d9132f6ca33bcd91c5dddb","tid":1553569,"uid":164378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T15:56:27.000Z","msg":"sorry 借位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n麻煩未食飯既同我入哂黎!!! 唔準有人餓住個肚!!!<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n《急推》 前線唔好餓死呀<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1540938\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1540938</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a555a8c33d70d4253526c348d022221b8afa92a1","tid":1553569,"uid":252132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T16:39:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nB2jkT8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnB2jkT8.png&h=a84c839d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n推 <br />\n有twitt